## ðŸ”¹ Dataset
- Source: [DataCo Supply Chain Dataset (Kaggle)](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/yogape/logistics-operations-database)  
- Raw dataset: 53 columns with detailed logistics operations.  
- Cleaned dataset: Reduced to ~10 essential fields for clarity and recruiter impact.  
- Key derived field: `shipping_delay` (difference between order date and ship date).  

